<item>
            <title>[FLINK-27255] Flink-avro does not support serialization and deserialization of avro schema longer than 65535 characters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-27255</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The underlying serialization of avro schema uses string serialization method of ObjectOutputStream.class, however, the default string serialization by ObjectOutputStream.class does not support handling string of more than 66535 characters (64kb). As a result, constructing flink operators that input/output Avro Generic Record with huge schema is not possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The purposed fix is two change the serialization and deserialization method of these following classes so that huge string could also be handled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/blob/master/flink-formats/flink-avro/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/formats/avro/typeutils/GenericRecordAvroTypeInfo.java#L107&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;GenericRecordAvroTypeInfo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/blob/master/flink-formats/flink-avro/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/formats/avro/typeutils/SerializableAvroSchema.java#L55&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;SerializableAvroSchema&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
